  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 797cf74cb972f7640a048711fad2e974, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 365d16e45ae2ca940bc1bd92db1ceba0, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: e3f22b4078761f74aacc0a3430c59fa5, type: 3}
  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: f36f82f84e7bb6c4c8b87baa55fb6f62, type: 3}
  audioSourceBabble: {fileID: 9205740816011340299}
  stopAudioSource: 1
  minPitch: 1
  maxPitch: 2
  frequency: 2
  textComponet: {fileID: 1032148383272698172}
  linesIntro1:
  - Well now... isn't this a sudden changeover?
  linesIntro: []
  linesIntro2:
  - "I see that you haven\u2019t been fired yet."
  - Good. That's good.
  - Consistency is important to me, and I would dread having to remember a new face
    again.
  linesIntro3:
  - "Let\u2019s cut to the chase, Little Goblin."
  - You and I both know each other decently by now, yes?
  linesPasstime:
  - You know me, little friend. don't keep me waiting.
  - Don't worry your little head on what I'm to do with these potions. Clock's ticking,
    anyhow.
  linesRight:
  - Good, grand even.
  - "...And you didn\u2019t even ask one question."
  linesWrong:
  - "Little Goblin\u2026 I expected better."
  - Please try harder the next time I see you.
  linesEnd:
  - Remember to keep your eyes and ears open, especially around these parts.
  - We'll see each other again.
  textSpeed: 0.05
  potion: {fileID: 2739027923484847869}
  text: {fileID: 8563190087433188785}
